
INTRODUCTION
============

libyafuse2, library of yet another fuse 2, is developed to support for file system, e.g., Ext4 and FAT in user space.


QUICK INSTALLATION
==================
1. Building for Makefile
   Run my-cmake-unix.sh on platform of UNIX/Linux
   OR
   Run my-cmake-win32.sh on platform of Windows

2. Compiling for libyafuse2
   Run my-build.sh on platform of UNIX/Linux
   OR
   Run .sln of Microsoft Visual Studio 2010 or above on platform of Windows.


